print('\nWrite a program to Calculate EMI')
P=int(input('Enter principle amount:'))
T=int(input('Enter time period:'))
R=float(input('Enter interest amount:'))
si=(P*T*R)/100
EMI=(si+P)/T*12
print('The EMI amount is:',EMI)

OUTPUT:
Write a program to Calculate EMI
Enter principle amount:100000
Enter time period:2
Enter interest amount:0.5
The EMI amount is: 606000.0
